Xen module
============

Xen Puppet module

Classes
-------

xen

    install the Xen needed packages and run the service


xen::package

    installs the xen packages


xen::service

    ensure that xen services are running


xen::boot

    ensure that Xen kernels loads by default in grub
    depends on the grub module


xen::tools

    installs xen-tools software


